                    website is at the user's own risk.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#0A1931] mb-6 mt-12">
                    6. Modifications
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[#0A1931] mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    BuildPro may revise these Terms of Service for its website
                    at any time without notice. By using this website, you are
                    agreeing to be bound by the then current version of these
                    Terms of Service.
