                    These Terms and Conditions are governed by and construed in
                    accordance with the laws of the United States, and you
                    irrevocably submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the
                    courts in that location.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#0A1931] mb-6 mt-12">
                    8. User Conduct
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[#0A1931] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                    You agree not to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#0A1931] mb-8 space-y-2">
                    <li>Harass, threaten, or intimidate any person</li>
                    <li>
                        Post or transmit any unlawful, threatening, abusive,
                        defamatory, obscene, or otherwise objectionable material
                    </li>
                    <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
                    <li>Interfere with the normal operation of the website</li>
                    <li>
                        Engage in any form of spam or unsolicited communications
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#0A1931] mb-6 mt-12">
                    9. Contact Information
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[#0A1931] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                    If you have any questions about these Terms of Service,
                    please contact us at:
                </p>
                <div class="bg-[#f5f5f5] p-6 rounded-lg text-[#0A1931]">
                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>BuildPro</strong></p>
                    <p class="mb-2">Email: legal@buildpro.com</p>
                    <p class="mb-2">Phone: (555) 123-4567</p>
                    <p>Address: 123 Main Street, City, State 12345</p>
                </div>
